## Net claim after review (thesis-ready phrasing)
Two candidate new individual 2-uniform star tilings (E1, E2 — both proven pinned) and ONE
candidate new one-parameter family (proven to flex for all alpha in (0, pi/3); in-ring members
a=1,2,3 all found by the engine, a=3 after closing the palette gap) — all "new" relative to
Myers 2009, the only known enumeration, which its author explicitly labels unchecked.
NOT "4 new tilings": E3/E4 (+ the a=3 sibling) are members of the same family.
